k(t)
x
\partial_t{u(x,t)}=\partial_x[k(t)\partial_xu(x,t)]
\partial_t{u(x,t)}=k(t)\partial_{xx}u(x,t)
u(0,t)=u_0,u(L,0)=u_L=u(x,0)
